h3. Bugfixes

Die folgenden NetHack-Bugs wurden in NetHack-De behoben:

* C343-19 Dipping acid in a fountain may not destroy the acid.
* C343-179 If a monster is killed or tamed while over water (or by a drawbridge) while carrying a potion of acid, the game may panic.
* C343-218 Applying a wielded cream pie can crash the game.
* C343-268 Used up potion of acid may end up in bones file. 
* C343-275 If a lit, wielded, candle or potion of oil burns out, the game may crash.
* C343-276 If a figurine auto-transforms while wielded or worn, the game may crash.
* C343-324 Cutting a long worm in two will crash the game if the cut takes the worm to 1 HP or if long worms had become extinct.
* SC343-11 It's possible to easily find the identity of a high priest on the Astral plane.
* SC343-12 Hero using telepathy can abuse Call on the Astral Plane.

